  "prompt": "Why did Quora acquire Parlio?",
  "response": "Quora acquired Parlio in 2017 to enhance its platform for knowledge sharing and to improve user engagement by leveraging Parlio's community-driven question-and-answer format. Parlio was known for its focus on high-quality discussions and inviting experts to share their insights on various topics. By integrating Parlio's features and expertise, Quora aimed to foster richer interactions among its users and expand its offerings in the knowledge-sharing space. The acquisition was part of Quora's broader strategy to build a more comprehensive, engaging platform for users seeking informative content.",
